        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">carbide ceramic that is a non-oxide ceramic composed of boron and carbon, known for its remarkable hardness and low density</skos:definition> <skos:definition xml:lang="zh">由硼和碳组成的非氧化物碳化物陶瓷，以其极高的硬度和低密度而闻名</skos:definition>
        <PMD_0050117>B₄C</PMD_0050117>
    </owl:Class>
    


