        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">nitride ceramic that is a non-oxide ceramic composed of aluminum and nitrogen, prized for its high thermal conductivity</skos:definition> <skos:definition xml:lang="zh">由铝和氮组成的非氧化物陶瓷，因其高热导率而备受推崇</skos:definition>
        <PMD_0050117>AlN</PMD_0050117>
    </owl:Class>
    


