        <skos:definition xml:lang="en">boride ceramic that is a non-oxide ceramic composed of titanium and boron, valued for its high hardness and melting point</skos:definition> <skos:definition xml:lang="zh">由钛和硼组成的非氧化物陶瓷，因其高硬度和高熔点而受重视</skos:definition>
        <PMD_0050117>TiB₂</PMD_0050117>
    </owl:Class>
    


    <!-- https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0050073 -->

